{"data":[{"DT_RowId":"row_1009","actcode":"1812006","name":"Greeting Cards Production & Distribution Services","desc":"Includes providing complete intermediary services between individuals and companies on one hand and the firms involved in designing, printing, packaging, distributing or publishing greeting cards. Items delivery can be made by hand, or by mail. Besides organizing the contractual aspects between different parties, the process involves supervising the implementation of all the related services.","type":"Professional","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1010","actcode":"3212002","name":"Imitation Jewellery Smithing","desc":"Includes manufacturing goldsmiths\u2019 articles, such as brooches, earnings, necklaces, bracelets, rings made from base metals plated with precious metals, or jewellery containing imitation stones such as imitation gems stones, imitation diamonds.","type":"Professional","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"requires office\/retail space","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1013","actcode":"3290024","name":"3D Printing Products Production ","desc":"Includes firms specialized in producing products by the 3D printing through creating designs of objects with AutoCAD software, then the printer creates a three-dimensional object using lasers to fuse powdered materials together layer by layer, the powdered materials involve metal, plastic, rubber, silicon, ceramic, such technology involves different products and parts such as, jewelry, industrial parts, vehicles, dental and medical industry.","type":"Professional","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"Office space","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1014","actcode":"4742002","name":"Radio, TV Stations, Cinema & Theater Equipment Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of cameras, lightings, projectors, loudspeakers and montage systems used in broadcasting stations and television studios, as well as cinema and theater and radio and television transmission.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1015","actcode":"4510102","name":"Buses & Trucks Trading","desc":"Includes reselling different passenger buses, as well as trucks and trailers for transporting goods, liquid substances, building materials\u2026etc.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1016","actcode":"4510103","name":"Specialized Vehicles Trading","desc":"Includes reselling specialized motor vehicles including ambulances, fire engines, garbage collectors , street sweepers, truck- mounted cranes for loading and discharging and truck mixers.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1017","actcode":"4510104","name":"Electric Cars Trading","desc":"Includes electric mini cars designed to serve in golf clubs, football stadiums, horse racetracks as well as passengers and visitors shuttles in airports and malls.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1019","actcode":"4510201","name":"Used Luxury Automobiles Trading","desc":"Includes selling of luxury automobiles distinguished with elite designs and finest engineering specifications and manufacturing accuracy and high prices production. This activity defines the factors for classifying luxury automobiles in terms of price and brand and the price must not be less than 700.000 AED","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1020","actcode":"4510202","name":"New Automobile Trading for Export","desc":"Includes firms dealing in exporting new cars only, these firms are not allowed to open shops and sell cars directly to the public as the activity no. 4510101 \u201cNew Motor Vehicles Trading\u201d.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1021","actcode":"4510902","name":"Used Trucks Trading","desc":"Includes reselling used trucks for transporting goods, building materials and liquid tankers\u2026etc","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1022","actcode":"4510907","name":"Classic Cars Trading","desc":"Includes selling older automobiles and which are distinguished by their respective fine design, high engineering standards and superior workmanship, the factors determine a car as a classic include engine displacement, custom coachwork and luxury accessories, power brakes, power clutch \u2026etc.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1023","actcode":"4510915","name":"Used Automobile Trading for Export","desc":"Includes firms dealing in exporting used cars only, these firms are not allowed to open shops and sell cars directly to the public as the activity no. 5010-04 \u201cUsed Automobile Trading\u201d.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1024","actcode":"4530001","name":"Auto Spare Parts & components Trading","desc":"Includes reselling spare parts and to use fully or partially in repairing and maintaining motor vehicles, buses, trucks and trailers and other relevant requisites including oils, detergents, paints.. etc..","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1025","actcode":"4530003","name":"Used Auto Spare Parts & Requisites Trading","desc":"Includes reselling the spare parts and components which cover the overall of the motor vehicle such as body parts and mirrors, brakes, suspension and steering, engine and drive train , exterior and interior accessories, headlights and lighting.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1026","actcode":"4530005","name":"Tyres & AccessoriesTrading","desc":"Includes reselling of various types of tyres and requisites including casings, rims and tubes.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1027","actcode":"4530008","name":"Batteries Trade","desc":"Includes reselling power generation and storage batteries for cars, boats, motorcycles and other machinery.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1028","actcode":"4530011","name":"Auto Accessories Trading","desc":"Includes the reselling accessories fitted in cars and vehicle exterior such as, additional bumpers to adjust the exterior, air deflectors to increase the car's efficiency, baggage loading racks to diversify the car's use, sun and rain protectors and small trailers, as well as the interior electronic and smart devices, also, devices fitted in public service vehicles such as police, ambulances and fire engines.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1029","actcode":"4540101","name":"Motorcycles Trade","desc":"Includes reselling the two or three wheeled motorized motorcycles for cruising in paved roads or for off road use, including selling spare parts and motorcyclists accessories such as helmets .","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1030","actcode":"4540102","name":"Motorcycles Spare Parts & Accessories Trading","desc":"Includes reselling the parts and components used for the repair or replacement of motorcycles failed parts, also the motorcyclists accessories such as helmets.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1031","actcode":"4540107","name":"Jet Ski Trading","desc":"Includes reselling personal watercraft used water recreational activities and sport.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1032","actcode":"4540110","name":"Scooters Trading","desc":"\u00a0Includes reselling the electric scooters which are equipped with battery to produce power. ","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1033","actcode":"4610005","name":"Authentic Artifacts & Antiques Auction House","desc":"Includes firms which conduct auctions of genuine artifacts, antiques and\/or artworks. Auctions may be held for either commercial or non-commercial purposes and may be held on behalf of a third party (e.g. art gallery, charity).","type":"Professional","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1034","actcode":"4610006","name":"Merchandising services","desc":"Includes firms engaged in displaying and presenting products in supermarkets and retail stores to maximize sales, including, wrapping some goods with gifts, pictures or cards to promote.","type":"Professional","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1035","actcode":"4610010","name":"Commercial Brokers","desc":"Includes firms engaged in bringing sellers and buyers involved in wholesale and retail trade together in return of a commission or remuneration, these firms are neither allowed to trade on own account nor practice brokerage in real estate, services, shares and bonds and finance.","type":"Professional","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1036","actcode":"4610011","name":"Turnkey Projects Contracting","desc":"Includes firm specialized in supplying private and governmental facilities like educational, military and health units, hotels, banks public departments, offshore firms and others with furniture, decorations, equipment, fixtures, appliances and utensils. Firms classified under this activity execute such services and the required installations either through direct contracting or by sub-contractors, these firms are permitted to directly import their materials, but not re-export or trade them.","type":"Professional","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1037","actcode":"4610012","name":"Discount Cards Services","desc":"Includes firms which provide other parties with cards that can be used to obtain reduced prices or certain facilities when buying products or services from a group of shops, hotels or other firms participating in the program of reduced prices or facilities provided by such cards, such firms are neither allowed impose charges for obtaining the cards nor to impose contracts on the customers against the provision of the service.","type":"Professional","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1038","actcode":"4620101","name":"Grains, Cereals & Legumes Trading","desc":"Includes reselling cereals and fruits such as rice, wheat, barley, corn, dates, citrus, legumes, beans, chick peas, and others. It also includes peeling, blending and bleaching for preparation before consumption.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1039","actcode":"4620206","name":"Tanned Leathers Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of tanned and processed animal leather to render for industrial or any other use.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1040","actcode":"4661010","name":"Fuel Supply Services","desc":"Includes firms engaged in supplying sea and land transport companies, industrial firms, power generating plants with fuel and lubricants and other similar materials to operate machinery and equipment.","type":"Professional","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1041","actcode":"4661011","name":"Compressed Natural Gas Trading","desc":"Includes selling compressed natural gas which is made by compressing natural gas to less than 1% of the volume it occupies at standard atmospheric pressure, and It is stored and distributed in hard containers in cylindrical or spherical shapes, it\u2019s as fuel that can be used in place of gasoline, diesel fuel and liquefied petroleum gas, it\u2019s used in traditional gasoline automobiles that have been modified or in vehicles specifically manufactured for CNG use, or in conjunction with another fuel such as Diesel (bi-fuel).","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1042","actcode":"4661101","name":"Trading Crude Oil Abroad","desc":"Includes the trading process carried outside the UAE for the crude oil before processing and refining into more useful products.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1043","actcode":"4661102","name":"Offshore Refined Oil Product Trading","desc":"Includes the trading process carried outside the UAE for the crude oil before processing and refining into more useful products.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1044","actcode":"4662001","name":"Metal Ores Trading","desc":"Includes reselling industrial basic ores for extracting various metals including hematite, bauxite, and zinc ore...etc.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1045","actcode":"4663101","name":"Building & Construction Materials Wholesale Trading","desc":"Includes wholesale merchants engaged in the wholesale trade building and construction materials to retailers, to industrial, commercial, professional users, this activity is exclusively available to firms intend to practice wholesaling in warehouses.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1046","actcode":"4669113","name":"Used Cooking Oils Trading","desc":"Includes selling waste cooking oils collected from restaurants in order to recycle and use in producing soap and biodiesel.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1047","actcode":"4669210","name":"Medical Gas Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of specially bottled gases for medical and treatment purposes, including oxygen, sterilization and anesthesia gases.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1048","actcode":"4669212","name":"Tannery & Dyeing Materials Trading","desc":"Includes reselling the solutions that contain dyes and particular chemical material used to add color to textile products, it also involves the acidic chemical compounds for treating skins of animals to produce leather.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1049","actcode":"4669213","name":"Acids & Alkalines Trading","desc":"Includes reselling acids and alkalines for producing other industrial products and compounds.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1050","actcode":"4669214","name":"Photography Processing Materials Trading","desc":"Includes reselling photography processing chemicals and photographs printing papers.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1051","actcode":"4669217","name":"Non Edible Oil Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of vegetable and animal non-edible oil used for industrial purposes.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1052","actcode":"4669218","name":"Adhesives Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of glass, metal, plastic, wood fixing adhesive, packs, boxes, carton boxes closing tapes, paper, tiles, flooring and cladding adhesives and tapes, and any other material not classified under glue and gum.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1053","actcode":"4669227","name":"Petrochemicals Trading","desc":"Includes the resale of petrochemicals derived from transforming refined oil derivatives and classified as light petrochemicals such as Olovires, Butylene, Ethylene, Probalene, aromatic compounds, Benzene, Toluene, Xylene Methanol, Formaldehyde, Ammonia and Urea, or intermediate petrochemicals such as Monovinyl chloride and final petrochemicals such as polyethylene, polyvinyl chloride, carbon and the Hydrogen.such products are used in various commercial and industrial as crude before any treatment or transformative operations.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1054","actcode":"4669911","name":"Raw Materials Trading","desc":"Includes reselling raw materials used in different processes manufacturing and handcrafting and which are only exploitable after going treatments, extraction or formation processes, they involve pulpwood to make papers, shells for shell handicrafts, extracts and natural herbs for perfumes, medicines and cosmetics, also minerals ores such as sand and rocks for extracting metals, and other similar raw materials. ","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1055","actcode":"4690003","name":"Caps & Lids Trading","desc":"Includes reselling different caps and lids seal the mouths of bottles and containers.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1056","actcode":"4690004","name":"Glass Bottles Trading","desc":"Includes reselling bottles made of glass and used to store liquids.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1057","actcode":"4690005","name":"Smelters & Furnaces Refractory Materials Trading","desc":"Includes reselling non-metallic materials having the properties of resisting high temperatures and are used in linings for furnaces, kilns, incinerators and reactors.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1058","actcode":"4690006","name":"Airline Inflight Products Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of various products specifically made for airlines to use including food trolleys, blankets, towels, cushions, plastic and metal cutlery, dishes and cups, toys and children items, paper products.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1059","actcode":"4690016","name":"Authentic Antiques, Artefacts & Artworks Trading","desc":"Includes firms trade in genuine antiques, artifacts and original artworks,, including paintings, drawings, sculptures, photographs, handicraft works, masterworks, and old antique cameras and accessories. Also includes promotional activities for these works such as advertising, public relations and events through a licensed media provider.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1060","actcode":"4690019","name":"Unique & Special Goods Trading","desc":"Includes firms engaged in the display and trade of unique and special goods such as antiques, frames, furnishings and other products, provided that the products displayed are limited quantities.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1061","actcode":"4690101","name":"Goods Wholesalers","desc":"Includes firms engaged in the wholesale of goods and products to retailers, to industrial, commercial, professional users, this activity is exclusively available to firms intend to practice wholesaling in warehouses only.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1062","actcode":"4721016","name":"Food Supplements Trading","desc":"Includes reselling the supplements which are classified as food and not drugs and are intended to provide nutrients which might be lacked in the food or otherwise not be consumed in sufficient quantities, it involves vitamins, minerals, fiber, fatty acids, or amino acids, honey and herbal tonics, nourishing substitutes for athletes and diet recipes.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1063","actcode":"4721035","name":"Flavours & Fragrances Trading","desc":"Includes reselling flavors and fruit extracts used in processing foodstuff, also fragrances used in manufacturing aromatics and cleaning products.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1064","actcode":"4721041","name":"Natural Herbs Trading","desc":"Includes reselling raw and dried plants, herbs tisanes and fruits used for medication and treatment, without involving any converting or industrial processes.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1065","actcode":"4730002","name":"Lubricants & Grease Trading","desc":"includes reselling the high viscosity oil based lubricating substances used for lessening friction in the working parts of a mechanism in order to protect against wear and transfer heat.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1066","actcode":"4741001","name":"Calculators & Spare Parts Trading","desc":"Includes reselling the device used to perform both basic and complex operations of arithmetic.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1067","actcode":"4741002","name":"Typewriters, Photocopiers & Spare Parts Trading","desc":"Includes reselling typewriters, photocopiers, stencil machines, microfilming machines, microfilm and projectors and copiers, as well as spare parts, ribbons, ink, chemicals and accessories.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1068","actcode":"4741003","name":"Computer Equipment Requisites Trading","desc":"Includes reselling computers and accessories, including servers, modems, monitors, and central processing units, printers, drawing and programmed discs, disc readers, and memory and file storage requisites.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1069","actcode":"4741004","name":"Computer Systems & Communication Equipment Software Trading","desc":"Includes reselling the set of application software and its documentation concerned with realizing the user\u2019s needs and problems, and is applicable in different domains, medicine, accounting, and engineering, it involves also the application software designed to run on smartphones and mobile devices.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1070","actcode":"4741006","name":"Computer & Data Processing Requisites Trading","desc":"Includes reselling tapes, CD-ROMs, ribbons, printers ink, paper and other requisites used in computer operation and data storage.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1071","actcode":"4741007","name":"Computer Electric Accessories Trading","desc":"Includes reselling computer electric accessories such as distributors, switches, surge suppressors and battery back-ups and cables and connectors","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1072","actcode":"4741011","name":"Mobile Phones & Accessories Trading","desc":"Includes reselling cellular phones which make and receive telephone calls over a radio link while moving around a wide geographic area, beside telephony they support a wide variety of services such as text messaging, email, Internet access, gaming and photography, it involves selling different accessories such as memory card, car chargers, batteries, leather cases, screen protectors, Bluetooth headset, data cables, silicone skins, holders\u2026etc.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1073","actcode":"4741017","name":"Encryption Software Trading","desc":"Includes reselling the software for encryption solutions that protect sensitive data across enterprise applications data processing IT, critical transactions, storage and big data platforms, ","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1074","actcode":"4741018","name":"Smart Machines & Spare Parts Trading","desc":"Includes reselling smart machines, such as, robots that apply artificial intelligence to enable them to think intelligently in the similar manner the intelligent humans think, and which can take the place of humans in dangerous environments, manufacturing, also, home automation systems that turn homes into smart homes. ","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1075","actcode":"4741022","name":"Satellite Receiving Equipment Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of systems and equipment receive radio and television transmission broadcasted by satellites or by special channels irreceivable by ordinary receivers or antennas.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1076","actcode":"4742001","name":"Audio-visual, Recording Equipment & Accessories Trading","desc":"Includes reselling audio-visual electronic equipment, involving radio sets, gramophones, loud-speakers television and video sets, cinematography projectors, slides projectors, instant translators respectively, also, cinematography and television photographing systems, as well as other non-commercial. Equipment used for photographing and recording inside studios or for commercial purposes are classified under Class 5150.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1077","actcode":"4742002","name":"Radio, TV Stations, Cinema & Theater Equipment Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of cameras, lightings, projectors, loudspeakers and montage systems used in broadcasting stations and television studios, as well as cinema and theater and radio and television transmission.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1078","actcode":"4742005","name":"Electric Vehicles Charging Stations & Systems & Spare Parts Trading","desc":"Includes reselling public charging stations used to supply electric energy for the recharging of electric vehicles that use electricity instead of conventional petrol, whether such stations located at retail shopping or public places or on-streets, as well as the same charging systems used for residential and offices charging.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1079","actcode":"4751001","name":"Textile Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of textiles and fabrics used for sewing and fashion wear or making readymade garments.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1080","actcode":"4751002","name":"Tents , Sheds & Tarpaulins Trading","desc":"Includes reselling tents and temporary and permanent sheds made of textiles or plastic and designed to be fixed in shops or building or streets, in order to protect against sun and rain, also, covers and tarpaulin for covering outdoor or transported cargo or for covering cars, it involves fixing these products said places.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1081","actcode":"4751003","name":"Sewing & Embroidery Requisites Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of tailoring threads, buttons and needles, as well as embroidery golden and silver threads, tiny diamonds, colored ribbons and others.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1082","actcode":"4751004","name":"Blankets, Towels & Linens Trade","desc":"Includes reselling household of blankets and linen, including bedcovers, furniture covers, bed sheets, towels, pillows, cushions and covers and all the other similar products.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1083","actcode":"4751015","name":"Threads & Yarns Trading","desc":"Includes reselling all kinds of threads for tailoring and embroidering garments, curtains, drapery and upholstery, also, includes cotton and wool yarns used in weaving and spinning industries.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1084","actcode":"4752001","name":"Timber Trading","desc":"Includes reselling timber prior to cutting into boards, bars or blocks to use in construction or in industry.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1085","actcode":"4752003","name":"Reinforcement Steel Bars Trading","desc":"Includes reselling steel bars commonly used as a tensioning device in reinforced concrete structures holding the concrete in compression.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1086","actcode":"4752004","name":"Sanitary Ware Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of sanitary wares, washbasins, bathtubs, Jacuzzi sets, lavatories taps, spigots, bathroom and kitchen articles (except furniture), as well as water drainage tubes, pipes, joints, drainage covering requisites and others.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1087","actcode":"4752005","name":"Tanks & Silos Trading","desc":"made of metal, plastic or reinforced fibers fixed in residential, commercial or industrial facilities for water, petroleum products, chemicals or other liquids, also, grain, seed silos, truck mounted tanks are classified under No. 503005.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1088","actcode":"4752006","name":"Electrical Fittings Trading","desc":"Includes reselling electric wires, cables, assembly boxes, distribution panels, poles, cable, ducts and communication wires. (related gauging devices are listed under 5150-11).","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1089","actcode":"4752007","name":"Bricks Trading","desc":"Includes reselling of bricks used in building and construction bricks made of lime, bricks, glass or any other material.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1090","actcode":"4752009","name":"Marble & Natural Stones Trading","desc":"Includes reselling varieties of marbles and natural stones like granite, basalt, limestone, this activity is limited to firms that trade these materials as crude before any conversional processes except cutting in blocks or slabs for transport purposes.","type":"Commercial","status":"Non-Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1091","actcode":"4752011","name":"Tiles & Flooring Materials Trading","desc":"Includes reselling different kinds of tiles, mosaic, ceramic, cement and interlock tiles, marble tiles, granite and basalt tiles, also, flooring materials made of rubber, plastic, wood or fibers to cover buildings and vehicles floor