ent","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1568","actcode":"4669104","name":"Waste Plastic Trading","desc":"Includes collecting and reselling all non- hazardous plastic waste, such as water bottles, boxes, shopping bags, dishes and food containers, after being used and disposed of by households, industrial and agricultural facilities, in order recycle and transform into new plastic products.","type":"Commercial","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Waste Management","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1569","actcode":"4669208","name":"Basic Industrial Chemicals Trade","desc":"Includes reselling intermediate chemicals such as resins, compounds, salts, sulfates, sulfurs, and others used in manufacturing by blending with other substances to produce paints, ink, cosmetics, detergents, fertilizers, pesticides, final chemical products, manufacturing metals, water purification and sterilization, in food industries such as preservatives, colorants, additives, flavors and fragrances, or in environment protection.","type":"Commercial","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Security Investigator Regulatory Agency - SIRA","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1570","actcode":"4669215","name":"Fire Extinguishing Materials Trading","desc":"Includes reselling fire control and extinguishing gases, foams and specially treated water, as well as these materials original chemicals.","type":"Commercial","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Dubai Civil Defense","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1571","actcode":"4669222","name":"Oilfield Chemicals Trading","desc":"Includes reselling chemicals for various oilfield applications like production, well stimulation, drilling and injection.","type":"Commercial","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Department of Petroleum Affairs","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1572","actcode":"4669230","name":"Water Treatment & Purification Chemicals Trading","desc":"Includes reselling the chemicals which purify water by assisting in the re