itime City Authority ","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1728","actcode":"7730020","name":"Aircraft & Requisites Leasing","desc":"Includes firms specialized in leasing airplanes under lease contracts for air flights in scheduled passenger and freight transport flights including its operational and ground handling tools.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Dubai Civil Aviation Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1729","actcode":"7911004","name":"Travel Agency","desc":"Includes any person who sells air tickets outbound trip, and provides related services including accommodation, visas, tours organizing and transportation, in addition to selling tourist programs organized by outbound tour operators.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Dubai Civil Aviation Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1730","actcode":"8010001","name":"Event Security & Bodyguard Services","desc":"Includes providing parties and other events with guards to care for the security aspects, organize visitors and keep order, as well as offering private guarding to individuals.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Security Investigator Regulatory Agency - SIRA","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1731","actcode":"8010013","name":"General Security Guard Services","desc":"Includes providing guarding services to facilities and residential and commercial buildings.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Security Investigator Regulatory Agency - SIRA","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1732","actcode":"8129007","name":"Yacht Cleaning Services","desc":"Includes yacht interior and exterior cleaning, involving buffing and polishing, metal restoration and polishing, teak brightening and oiling, plastic enclosure cleaning and polishing, interior cleaning, leather and vinyl treatment.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Dubai Maritime City Authority ","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1733","actcode":"8230008","name":"Sports Exhibitions Organizing","desc":"Includes firms specialized in organizing sport exhibitions for official departments and sport clubs in order to promote sport activities and facilities, as well as for commercial entities engaged in sport products and services.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"General Authority of Youth & Sports Welfare","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1734","actcode":"8542007","name":"Fine Arts Training","desc":"Includes institutions primarily engaged in offering instruction in performing arts, involving theatrical representation, music, singing, speech, simulation, dance, also, arts and handicraft training, such as drawing, sculpture, calligraphy, floral arts, glass crafts, embossing, fine arts printing, pottery \u2026etc.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Knowledge and Human Development Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1735","actcode":"8549001","name":"Automobile Driving School","desc":"Includes providing theoretical education and practical driving instruction on light motor, heavy trucks and buses, lifting trucks and motorcycles, before attempting the practical driving test conducted by the concerned authorities.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Road & Transport Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1736","actcode":"8549008","name":"Aviation Training Services","desc":"Includes firms specialized in training and qualifying individuals to perform technical occupations in aviation.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Dubai Civil Aviation Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1737","actcode":"8549009","name":"Child Skills Development Training","desc":"Includes institutions engaged in the provision of instruction which enriches and develops the non-academic skills of students by providing them with tools to sup