titutions primarily engaged in offering language instruction, including sign language and cultural awareness.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Knowledge & Human Development Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1742","actcode":"8549043","name":"Technical and Occupational Skills Training","desc":"Includes institutions primarily engaged in offering technical training in a variety of job-specific subjects and trades, the training often leads to job-specific certification, the areas of training include media production, hospitality and tourism, food safety and hygiene, agriculture, home economics, fashion design, cosmetic and hair care, healthcare, architecture, mechanics and built environment, construction including the installation of drywall for moistures resistance and acoustic absorption.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Knowledge & Human Development Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1743","actcode":"8549044","name":"Security Training Institute","desc":"Includes organizing seminars, conventions, conferences and meetings and workshops for security personnel.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Knowledge & Human Development Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1744","actcode":"8549045","name":"Transport Services Training","desc":"Includes providing practical training to the new firms engaged in transportation, or to businesses already practicing different modes of transport, such as, logistics, hazardous, international, light and heavy, passenger and tourist transport.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Knowledge & Human Development Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1745","actcode":"8549101","name":"Aviation Training Institute","desc":"Includes institutes engaged in providing ground as well as flying training in order to acquire air transport pilot license as per the curriculum and standards laid down by civil aviation authority, the courses involve aircraft general knowledge, principles of flights, general navigation, operational procedures, airplane performance, communication.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Dubai Civil Aviation Authority","appr2":"Knowledge & Human Development Authority"},{"DT_RowId":"row_1746","actcode":"8550006","name":"Education Support Services","desc":"Includes institutions primarily engaged in providing non-instructional services that support educational processes or systems, such as educational consultancies, university admission services academic liaison, educational facilities management as well as the provision of examination preparation","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Knowledge & Human Development Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1747","actcode":"8550007","name":"Educational Quality Assurance Services","desc":"Includes firms primarily engaged in assuring the quality of the delivery and assessment of the Technical and Vocational Education and Training qualifications (TVET) according to the requirements of the qualifications.","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Knowledge & Human Development Authority","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1750","actcode":"8890005","name":"Early Intervention Center","desc":"Includes the centers engaged in providing rehabilitation and assessment to children with developmental delays or to children with disabilities or eligible to from (aged birth to five years)","type":"Professional","status":"Regulated","prop":"","notes":"","appr1":"Ministry of Community Development","appr2":""},{"DT_RowId":"row_1751","actcode":"9000904","name":"Art Gallery","desc":"Includes galleries which constantly show art works such as drawings, sculptures, photographs, handicraft works, masterworks etc. or allocate these works of art for holding exhibitions for artists from time to time.\u00a0","type":"P